stories.title: Disciplined Bangladesh make it 4-0
stories.subTitle: Bangladesh v Zimbabwe, 4th ODI, Dhaka
stories.summary: Set 147 to win after yet another disciplined bowling attack, Bangladesh cruised through to their fourth win on the trot against a hapless Zimbabwe at the newly inaugurated Shere Bangla Stadium in Dhaka
